er’s arse. - Egg', 39634, 0), (222168, 'I am not a hero. Heroes do not cheat.', 39635, 0), (222169, 'No. I meant stay with me today. And tomorrow. And every day after.', 3253, 0), (222170, 'You are all that exists on the earth and under the sky that I do love. - Keiran', 39, 0), (222171, 'If I say that you are mine, then I am yours.', 39635, 0), (222172, 'We are young and the night is young. We are in the middle of somewhere and we are feeling everything.', 251, 0), (222173, 'Her eyes flashed, hot and angry, like lightening cutting through a red sunset.', 39636, 0), (222174, 'Although richer and Number 1 in the charts at this very moment, I’ve come full circle; once again I am the lanky, ginger, friendless geek.- Egg', 39634, 0), (222175, 'I told Jerome I will ring Egg every day because he’s my pal and not because I want him back in the band to write our second album. - Clipper', 39634, 0), (222176, 'If I had known how easy it is to lose your life, I would have treasured mine better".', 39637, 0), (222177, 'You truly do have the power to reach your goals.', 39638, 0), (222178, 'You’re unstoppable as long as you keep taking the next step.', 39638, 0), (222179, 'Your supporters can help you think in new ways, solve problems, and burst through barriers.', 39638, 0), (222180, 'There are 1,440 minutes in every day. How are you using yours?', 39638, 0), (222181, 'The most meaningful hopes and dreams don’t come from outside sources—they come from within.', 39638, 0), (222182, 'To make your goals savvy, keep them both personal (meaningful to you and aligned with your values) and positive (so you feel good about what you’re trying to accomplish.', 39638, 0), (222183, 'If you can find time for [other] activities, you can make time for your goals.', 39638, 0), (222184, 'When going for your goals, staying motivated, enthusiastic, and flexible are daily deeds of daring.', 39638, 0), (222185, 'Attitude plays a bigger role than you may imagine in determining your future success—bigger than talent, money, or popularity.', 39638, 0), (222186, 'The more often you visualize your success and the more details you envision, the more motivated you’ll feel.', 39638, 0), (222187, 'No matter how much (or how little) help someone provides, always say thanks. Thank yous are simple but important.', 39638, 0), (222188, 'It’s up to you to make your dreams real.', 39638, 0), (222189, 'If all else fails, try to get some sleep…whether you realize it or not, getting enough sleep can make it easier to solve problems, control your emotions, and cope with change.', 39638, 0), (222190, 'Ask yourself exactly what you want in your life—now and in the future. If you were given the opportunity to do or have anything, what would it be, and why?', 39638, 0), (222191, 'The biggest regrets people have aren’t about what they did, but what they didn’t do.', 39638, 0), (222192, 'Your values form the foundation of your life. They also form the foundation of your dreams. And just as each person’s values are unique, so are each person’s dreams.', 39638, 0), (222193, 'The contrast between the realization of his neglect and the fondness I had for my father was painful".', 39637, 0), (222194, 'You’ve become a miserable bastard and I can’t deal with it anymore.”Bex on Egg – Book 2 “Having it', 39634, 0), (222195, 'What''s wrong with all black?"Egg - Book 1 "Making it', 39634, 0), (222196, 'I will not give up. I must not fail."Burt, Book 1 "Making it', 39634, 0), (222197, 'No stone was left unturned in the unearthing of musical masterpieces."About Egg, Book 1 "Making it', 39634, 0), (222198, 'His mind buzzed, excited by new possibilities."About Egg, Book 1 "Making it', 39634, 0), (222199, 'She told me I couldn''t just put on a leather jacket and think I was rock''n''roll, I had to live it."Burt about Bex, Book 1 "Making it', 39634, 0), (222200, 'My old man tells me every chance he gets I’m “style over substance” and that I’ve never done anything of value in my life. I’m fifteen. What