in stops crawling.', 18, 0), (222974, 'It’s alright, Kitten,” Bones said. “He won’t shoot.”	Tate lowered his gun, even as the sudden dizziness from blood-loss made me sway.	Bones took my gun and casually handed it to Juan, who gapped at him in amazement. 	“You called her Kitten? And she let you? She put me in a coma for three days when I called her that. My balls never recovered from her smashing them into my spine.”	“And well she should have,” Bones agreed. “She’s mine. Kitten, and no one else’s.', 120, 0), (222975, 'A conclusion is the place you get to when you’re tired of thinking.', 6437, 0), (222976, 'Not really a party until someone brings the surprise zombies.', 2314, 0), (222977, 'I didn''t do it,'' he insisted.''Then why did you run?'' Sabrina asked.''And send rabbits to eat us! I''m a seven-year-old girl,'' Daphne said. ''Do you know how important bunny rabbits are to me?', 2409, 0), (222978, 'As far as he was concerned, there were only two good positions for a human. A female on her back. And a male facedown not breathing.', 108, 0), (222979, 'Some people make things happen. Some people watch things happen. And then there are those who wonder, ''What the hell just happened?', 1399, 0), (222980, 'Bad artists always admire each others work.', 40, 0), (222981, 'Wroth, darling,” she purred, smiling so sweetly. “I can’t wait for the next time I get to put my mouth on you.” In an instant the smile faded and she snapped her teeth and yanked her head back as if she was chewing something free.', 2157, 0), (222982, 'We have met the enemy and he is us.', 39770, 0), (222983, 'You should go." "I can''t." "Because you want to stare at the monster?" Alec''s green eyes blaze, but with a wholly human fire now. "Or because you pity me?" I couldn''t guess which possibility he loathes more. I fold my arms. "I can''t leave because the door''s locked. Believe me, I would''ve gone hours ago if I could have." "Oh. Of course." Then he looks so abashed--so boyish, and so handsome-